whereas.text:
Whereas science, technology, engineering and mathematics
			 are an essential element of the future competitiveness in the world of the
			 United States;

Whereas advances in technology have resulted in
			 significant improvement in the daily lives of people in the United
			 States;

Whereas scientific discoveries are critical to curing
			 diseases, solving global challenges, and expanding our understanding of our
			 world;

Whereas invigorating the interest of the next generation
			 of Americans in STEM education is necessary to maintain the global
			 competitiveness of the United States;

Whereas nations around the world have held science
			 festivals which have brought together hundreds of thousands of visitors
			 celebrating science;

Whereas science and engineering festivals have attracted
			 millions of participants and inspired a national effort to promote science and
			 engineering;
